## Required skills:
* knowledge and understanding of the search engine’s algorithm;
* work experience with SEO services and programs (Google Planner, Google Search Console, Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel, Bright Local, Spyfu, Ahrefs);
* the basics of copywriting;
* skills of useful content creation;
* creative thinking.
## Responsibilities include:
* search engine optimization – the site should remain high in the search results;
* report on the work undertaken;
* determining the project execution deadlines;
* assignment of tasks among team members;
* motivation of employees, promotion of their professional and career growth.
## Apply for the vacancy
If you are responsible, sociable, eager to develop in the field of SEO, and speak English fluently, leave the application below, we will definitely contact you!.  
## Advantages of working in our company:
* Good, stable salary
* Career opportunities
* On-the-job training
* Young, professional, positive, and friendly team
* Convenient work schedule
